01:18.946 --> 01:20.147
BROADER RESPONSE TO THE

01:20.147 --> 01:21.048
REFUGEES' ARRIVAL.

01:21.048 --> 01:22.950
YOU'VE BEEN THERE IN HUNGARY ALL

01:22.950 --> 01:23.617
WEEK.

