01:29.823 --> 01:30.624
>> Reporter: WELL, HUNGARY IS

01:30.624 --> 01:31.425
TRYING TO DO EVERYTHING IT

01:31.425 --> 01:32.960
POSSIBLY CAN TO SHUT THAT DOOR.

01:32.960 --> 01:35.595
THE PRIME MINISTER HAS BEEN VERY

01:35.595 --> 01:36.396
CRITICAL OF THE WAY THE

01:36.396 --> 01:37.564
EUROPEANS HAVE RESPONDED TO THE

01:37.564 --> 01:38.899
MIGRANT CRISIS.

01:38.899 --> 01:41.201
HE IS ARGUING FOR HIS COUNTRY

01:41.201 --> 01:42.970
AND EUROPE AS A WHOLE THIS IS

01:42.970 --> 01:45.138
ABOUT THEM DEFENDING THE

01:45.138 --> 01:46.606
CHRISTIAN IDENTITY OF THE

01:46.606 --> 01:48.742
LARGELY MUSLIM GROUP OF REFUGEES

01:48.742 --> 01:49.843
COMING TO EUROPE.

01:49.843 --> 01:51.244
AND HE HAS DONE MORE THAN

01:51.244 --> 01:53.280
ANY OTHER EUROPEAN NATION TO DO

01:53.280 --> 01:54.548
EVERYTHING HE CAN TO STOP THOSE

01:54.548 --> 01:55.449
PEOPLE ARE COMING.

01:55.449 --> 01:56.616
HE'S BUILDING A FENCE ALONG THE

01:56.616 --> 01:58.352
BORDER IN SYRIA, AND HE'S

