02:06.626 --> 02:08.729
SO AT THIS MEETING ON MONDAY IN

02:08.729 --> 02:10.430
BRUSSELS, THE HUNGARIANS AND THE

02:10.430 --> 02:11.231
HUNGARIAN POSITION IS GOING TO

02:11.231 --> 02:12.566
BE ONE OF THE BIGGEST THORNS IN

02:12.566 --> 02:15.035
THE SIDE OF THE E.U. MINISTERS

02:15.035 --> 02:16.470
WHO ARE TRYING TO GET SOME KIND

02:16.470 --> 02:18.238
OF A CONSENSUS HERE.

02:18.238 --> 02:20.540
>> Sreenivasan: THE E.U. IS

02:20.540 --> 02:22.009
PROPOSING A QUOTA SYSTEM WHERE

02:22.009 --> 02:23.944
DIFFERENT NATIONS WOULD ACCEPT

02:23.944 --> 02:25.412
DIFFERENT NUMBERS OF REFUGEES

