YESTERDAY, THE E.U. TRIED TO GET

02:38.725 --> 02:39.993
SEVERAL CENTRAL EUROPEAN NATIONS

02:39.993 --> 02:41.695
TO AGREE ON A TENTATIVE

02:41.695 --> 02:42.863
AGREEMENT WITH REGARD TO THIS

02:42.863 --> 02:44.664
QUOTA PLAN AND THAT WAS

02:44.664 --> 02:45.065
REJECTED.

