THE TRICKY PART OF ALL OF THIS

02:46.266 --> 02:48.301
IS THE NUMBERS KEEP GETTING

02:48.301 --> 02:49.336
BIGGER AND BIGGER.

02:49.336 --> 02:52.272
THE E.U. RIGHT NOW IS HAGGLING

02:52.272 --> 02:53.907
WITH THE ISSUE OF TRYING TO

02:53.907 --> 02:54.941
SETTLE THE REFUGEES OVER THE

02:54.941 --> 02:55.675
NEXT TWO YEARS.

