EARLIER THIS WEEK, THE U.N. PUT

02:58.679 --> 03:01.848
OUT AN ESTIMATE THAT WE WILL SEE

03:01.848 --> 03:02.716
850,000 PEOPLE COMING IN OVER

03:02.716 --> 03:04.518
THIS YEAR AND NEXT YEAR, SO THE

03:04.518 --> 03:05.685
NUMBERS KEEP SNOWBALLING AND

03:05.685 --> 03:07.254
THERE IS ACTUALLY SOME CONCERN

03:07.254 --> 03:09.423
AS THESE NUMBERS GROW BIGGER AND

03:09.423 --> 03:11.058
BIG THEY'RE THAT GROWING NUMBER

03:11.058 --> 03:12.392
COULD EVEN UNDERMINE SOME OF THE

03:12.392 --> 03:13.894
GOOD WILL THAT EXISTS IN SOME OF

03:13.894 --> 03:16.329
THE FRIENDLIER NATIONS,

03:16.329 --> 03:18.098
SO-CALLED FRIENDLIER NATIONS,

03:18.098 --> 03:19.966
LIKE SWEDEN AND GERMANY, THAT IF

03:19.966 --> 03:21.401
THEY SEE INCREASE NUMBERS OF

03:21.401 --> 03:22.502
PEOPLE COMING TO THEIR BORDERS

03:22.502 --> 03:24.371
THEY MIGHT GET COLD FEET ABOUT

03:24.371 --> 03:25.539
THIS WHOLE IDEA.

03:25.539 --> 03:26.306
>> Sreenivasan: YOU SPENT A

03:26.306 --> 03:27.507
WEEK THIS WEEK TALKING WITH

03:27.507 --> 03:28.208
SEVERAL REFUGEES.

03:28.208 --> 03:29.476
WHAT HAVE YOU BEEN HEARING FROM

03:29.476 --> 03:31.144
THEM ABOUT WHY THEY'RE COMING,

03:31.144 --> 03:32.546
WHY THEY'RE TAKING THIS RISK ON

03:32.546 --> 03:34.648
THIS JOURNEY OR WHY NOW AFTER

03:34.648 --> 03:35.182
YEARS OF WAR.

03:35.182 --> 03:36.283
>> QUITE SIMPLY, IT'S BEEN THE

03:36.283 --> 03:37.417
SYRIAN CIVIL WAR.

03:37.417 --> 03:38.952
THE MAJORITY OF PEOPLE WE MET

03:38.952 --> 03:40.821
WERE SYRIANS AND THEY SAID THEY

03:40.821 --> 03:41.988
LEFT THEIR COUNTRY BECAUSE OF

03:41.988 --> 03:43.256
THE VIOLENCE TEARING THEIR

03:43.256 --> 03:44.724
COUNTRY APART FOR THE LAST FIVE

03:44.724 --> 03:45.826
YEARS.

03:45.826 --> 03:46.993
WE MET A FATHER EARLIER THIS

03:46.993 --> 03:48.829
WEEK WHO TOLD ME A STORY ABOUT

03:48.829 --> 03:49.763
HIS FOUR-YEAR-OLD DAUGHTER.

03:49.763 --> 03:50.564
HE WAS TRAVELING WITH HIS

03:50.564 --> 03:51.698
FOUR-YEAR-OLD AND A

03:51.698 --> 03:52.432
THREE-YEAR-OLD.

03:52.432 --> 03:53.733
HE SAID HIS FOUR-YEAR-OLD

03:53.733 --> 03:55.469
DAUGHTER IS NOW RELUCTANT TO LET

03:55.469 --> 03:56.837
HIM WALK OUT THE DOOR ANY TIME

03:56.837 --> 03:58.238
BECAUSE SHE'S NOT SURE HE IS

03:58.238 --> 03:59.706
GOING TO COME BACK IN.

03:59.706 --> 04:01.174
I THINK IF YOU'RE A FATHER, IF

04:01.174 --> 04:03.009
YOU'RE ANY PARENT, AND THE WAR

04:03.009 --> 04:04.478
ALL AROUND YOU HAS GOTTEN SO

04:04.478 --> 04:05.245
PERVASIVE THAT YOUR

04:05.245 --> 04:06.413
FOUR-YEAR-OLD DAUGHTER IS AFRAID

04:06.413 --> 04:07.747
TO LET YOU GO OUT THE DOOR TO

04:07.747 --> 04:09.182
WORK IN THE MORNING, I THINK

04:09.182 --> 04:10.117
MOST PARENTS WOULD AGREE THAT'S

04:10.117 --> 04:11.751
A GOOD REASON TO LEAVE YOUR LIFE

04:11.751 --> 04:14.287
BEHIND.

04:14.287 --> 04:16.389
>> Sreenivasan: PEOPLE HAVE

04:16.389 --> 04:19.426
BEEN FLEEING SYRIA SINCE THE WAR

04:19.426 --> 04:22.696
STARTED 4 AND A HALF YEARS AGO.

04:22.696 --> 04:23.430
>> Reporter: THE SYRIAN

04:23.430 --> 04:24.731
REFUGEE CRISIS IS NOT A NEW

04:24.731 --> 04:25.065
THING.

04:25.065 --> 04:26.133
IT'S BEEN GOING ON AS LONG AS

04:26.133 --> 04:30.504
THE SYRIAN WAR, WHICH IS 2011.

04:30.504 --> 04:33.039
THE THING THAT IS NEW IS WHERE

04:33.039 --> 04:34.341
THE REFUGEES ARE GOING.

04:34.341 --> 04:36.042
FOR YEARS THE REFUGEES SIMPLY

04:36.042 --> 04:37.944
POURED INTO THE BORDERING ARAB

04:37.944 --> 04:39.913
STATES-- JORDAN, TURKEY, AND

04:39.913 --> 04:40.947
LEBANON.

04:40.947 --> 04:42.249
AND THE NUMBER THERE ARE PRETTY

04:42.249 --> 04:43.049
STAGGERING.

04:43.049 --> 04:44.551
IT'S ESTIMATED THAT THREE TO

04:44.551 --> 04:46.052
FOUR MILLION PEOPLE HAVE NOW

04:46.052 --> 04:47.687
FLED SYRIA AND GONE INTO THOSE

04:47.687 --> 04:48.622
NATIONS.

04:48.622 --> 04:49.523
IF YOU LOOK AT PLACES LIKE THE

04:49.523 --> 04:51.291
SATARI REFUGEE CAMP IN JORDAN,

04:51.291 --> 04:53.160
IT HAS BECOME ONE OF THE BIGGEST

04:53.160 --> 04:54.995
CITIES IN THAT ENTIRE COUNTRY.

04:54.995 --> 04:55.929
SO WHILE THE NUMBERS COMING TO

04:55.929 --> 04:57.898
EUROPE ARE LARGE, THEY PALE IN

04:57.898 --> 05:02.302
COMPARISON.

05:02.302 --> 05:03.303
>> Sreenivasan: WILLIAM

05:03.303 --> 05:04.070
BRANGHAM JOINING US FROM

05:04.070 --> 05:06.106
AUSTRIA, THANKS SO MUCH.

05:06.106 --> 05:07.741
>> THANKS, HARI.

05:07.741 --> 05:08.542
>> Sreenivasan: AS MANY

05:08.542 --> 05:10.076
AS 10,000 MIGRANTS ARE EXPECTED

05:10.076 --> 05:11.912
TO ARRIVE IN MUNICH TODAY.

