THEY'RE EXPECTING ANOTHER 7,000

06:05.398 --> 06:07.033
OR SO BY THE END OF THE DAY, AND

06:07.033 --> 06:09.436
THE GERMAN FOREIGN MINISTER SAID

06:09.436 --> 06:10.503
YESTERDAY THAT THERE COULD BE AS

06:10.503 --> 06:13.373
MANY AS 40,000 WHO COME IN THIS

06:13.373 --> 06:13.974
WEEKEND.

