TO, I'D DO IT AT THE DROP OF A

14:40.913 --> 14:42.014
DIME, BECAUSE EVERYONE MADE ME

14:42.014 --> 14:42.882
FEEL LIKE THAT'S WHAT- THAT'S

14:42.882 --> 14:44.250
ALL I WAS WORTH.

